July 28, 2017 7:02 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Psagot Securities Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Psagot Securities Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, corporations, public institutes, and non-profit organizations. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. For the fixed income portion, it invests in corporate bonds. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was founded in 1963 and is based in Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel. Psagot Securities Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Psagot Investment House Ltd.


16th Floor14 Ahad Ha'Am StreetTel Aviv-Yafo,  65142IsraelFounded in 1963



Phone: 972 3 7968805

Fax: 972 3 7968889

