Psagot is Israel's largest investment house.  On behalf of its close to one million private investors, business clients and institutional clients, Psagot manages approximately 186*  billion NIS.The investment house offers its clients a wide range of investment tracks and investment instruments adapted to meet investors' various needs and in addition offers life insurance products to suit diverse objectives. Psagot Investment House is owned by Apax Partners.  read more>>Management Members >>Corporate Responsibility>> Variety of Solutions>> Institutional Involvement>> Service Level Agreement>>   Psagot's knowledge center for financial education The most important financial tool is knowledge. Psagot Investment House, the largest manager of public monies in Israel provides its 1.3 million clients and the public access to Psagot's knowledge center for financial education.  The center furnishes various innovative and advanced tools in financial and economic areas, in an effort to assist in the management of monies and minimize common financial investment errors.To Psagot Knowledge Center>>   


		  





















































	
